comp-kkffz63c.html: HARASSMENT AND VIOLENCE CAN HAPPEN TO ANYONE, ANYTIME

comp-kkfg2e9g.html: WE'RE ON A MISSION TO END HARASSMENT IN ALL ITS FORMS

comp-kkfc4g4u.html: GET Trained

comp-kkfc4g4u1.html: Get trained today and train many others as well. Join the community to get  empowered and empower others. Register to our upcoming free online campaign.

comp-kkfc4g4u4.html: With our organization’s mission always in mind, we strive to find new strategies for dealing with this challenge. Advocacy is something that we take very seriously, and our team is working each and every day to make a positive impact and constantly updating our training program. Contact us to learn more about our commitment to this cause.

comp-kkfc4g4u6.html: SUPPORT

comp-kkfc4g4u7.html: At Athena, we are dedicated to stepping up our efforts in addressing this issue. Support is by no means an easy feat, but through cooperation and community empowerment we believe we can facilitate progress in this area. We are always striving to make a difference, and invite you to learn more and lend your support.

comp-kkfc4g4s6.html: Athena is a photoblog and grassroots initiative to raise awareness about and combat  harassment by posting photographs and narrative accounts of individuals' encounters. We believe  that by working together we could overcome our challenges much more efficiently, and that is why we ultimately decided to launch Athena.

comp-kkfc4g4t5.html: We have a two bridge model. First we create a community forum where people can express and freely share their experiences because we are here to hear you. Second we train using various techniques like bystander intervention methods to students, women, men of all ages by providing free training experience.  We believe that everyone deserves the resources to respond to, prevent and intervene in instances of harassment.
